> Please note that the turkey and sides will ship in separate boxes.

> This complete holiday feast is one more thing to add to your list of things to be thankful for!

> Download recipe card for complete nutrition information.

> Accompanying sides include Creamy Mashed Potatoes, fluffy Brioche Stuffing, roasted Garlic Green Beans, Fresh Cranberry Sauce, and warm Apple Crisp with Cinnamon Pecan Crumble for dessert.

== Roast Turkey with Garlic Herb Butter Rub and Classic Gravy ==

Follow our 4-hour dinner game plan included in the comprehensive instruction booklet
(complete with a turkey carving guide!) for a same-day Thanksgiving dinner using
@Honest Turkey® Frozen Whole Turkey{1%14 lb} with @Roasted Garlic Herb Butter{1%oz}
rubbed under the skin.

Prepare the Classic Gravy with @Chicken Stock Concentrate{9.6%g}, @Chicken Demi-Glace{1},
and @Flour{1/2%cup}.

== Creamy Mashed Potatoes ==

Cook @Potatoes{1%lb} until tender, mash with @Sour Cream{23%g} and @Milk{8%oz}.

== Garlic Green Beans ==

Roast @Green Beans{6%oz} with @Garlic{1} and @Pecans{1/2%oz}.

== Fresh Cranberry Sauce ==

Combine @Cranberries{12%oz}, @Dried Cranberries{1%oz}, @Orange{1}, and @Lemon{1}.

== Brioche Stuffing ==

Stuff @Brioche Buns{2} with @Shallot{2%oz}, @Celery Sticks{2.5%oz}, @Eggs{2},
@Yellow Onion{1}, @Garlic Powder{1%tsp}, @Sage{1/4%oz}, and @Thyme{1/4%oz}.

== Apple Crisp with Cinnamon Pecan Crumble ==

Top @Granny Smith Apple{1}(peeled and sliced) with @?Cinnamon{1%tsp} and
@Brown Sugar{1%tbsp}.